{
  "texts": [
    "For fine-tuning, we use LoRA, a parameter-efficient technique that has shown comparable performance to fine-tuning all parameters (Hu et al., 2021).",
    "Further details about the parameters are reported in §A.2.",
    "We conduct a comparative study on the impact of in-context learning and fine-tuning to adapt LLMs 2 https://github.com/langchain-ai/langchain for dialogues.",
    "We select Llama2 C and Mistral I as base LLMs and experiment in four dialogue types: ODDs, KGDs, TODs, and QA.",
    "For each dialogue type, we study the impact of external knowledge, both retrieved and gold."
  ]
}